<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Research Report: {{ $('Generate PDF HTML').item.json.topic }}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear Immanuel,</p>
      <p>I hope this email finds you well. I am pleased to share with you a comprehensive research report on "<strong>
{{ $('Generate PDF HTML').item.json.topic }}</strong>", generated on <strong>{{ $('Generate PDF HTML').item.json.formattedDate }}</strong>.</p>
      <p>This report provides an in-depth analysis, including a detailed introduction, summary, key findings, news highlights, scholarly insights, and a Wikipedia summary, all supported by credible sources. It is designed to offer valuable insights and actionable information to support your research, decision-making, or project needs.</p>
      <p>Please find the report attached as a PDF for your review. Should you have any questions, require further details, or wish to discuss the findings, feel free to reach out‚ÄîI‚Äôd be happy to assist.</p>
